## Resolved Decisions

- SPAR is **default tier**, not special
- Shoprite: `startswith "shoprite"` (case-insensitive), verified on sample file
- Pistola: try mapped group first; fallback when direct total is **0**
- Total column hidden when orders loaded; negative shortfall shown on **0-4** bucket
- Show rows with negative **or** positive values when orders loaded
